Package: CEOdata
Title: Datasets of the CEO (Centre d'Estudis d'Opinio) for Opinion Polls in Catalonia
Version: 1.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xavier", "Fernández-i-Marín", , "xavier.fim@gmail.com", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9522-8870")),
    person("Joel", "Ardiaca", email = "joelardiacaarnau@gencat.cat", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-4937-8941")))
Description: Easy and convenient access to the datasets of the
  "Centre d'Estudis d'Opinio", the Catalan institution for polling and public
  opinion. The package retrieves microdata directly from the open data platform
  of the Generalitat de Catalunya and returns it in a tidy format.
Depends:
  R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
  tibble,
  haven,
  dplyr (>= 1.0.0),
  urltools,
  stringr,
  jsonlite
Suggests:
  knitr,
  ggplot2,
  tidyr (> 1.1.1),
  curl,
  rmarkdown,
  vtable,
  compareGroups
